text: Nallathangal Dam is a dam Near Dharapuram in Tirupur district of Tamil Nadu, south India. == Construction == The dam was constructed of across the Nallathangal odai near bhagavan kovil, Dharapuram Taluk in the year 2007. It is 12 km away from Dharapuram town. http://tiruppur.tn.nic.in/dams.html ==References== Category:Dams in Tamil Nadu Category:Dams completed in 2007 Category:Embankment dams Category:Tirupur district
